{"id":232977258,"title":"❗️買不到口罩請別太驚慌❗️","content":"身為超商店員\n這兩天10個客人走進來有11個是要買口罩的\n聽到口罩賣完的大家表情都很慌張💦\n一直問那怎麼辦？哪邊還可以買？！\n從1/28-1/30 政府每天都會釋出600萬個口罩給四大超商，每人限購三個！陸續也會提供各大藥妝店。\n！！這些是之前的庫存釋出的！！\n開工之後廠商會恢復產能，即可穩定供貨！\n大家不要太驚慌，在這邊也呼籲大家不要一次買太多囤著，可能會造成有急需的人沒有口罩用😷\n之後慢慢都會有口罩可以買的！\n因為限購的關係有少數不滿的聲音出現，也有客人直接說「那我重新排隊還不是一樣要賣我？」\n在這邊真的希望大家能互相體諒～也盡量不要做重複排隊的舉動🥺\n大家一起加油，努力防疫！\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/264cf8d5-6b8e-4013-aeb9-bf0349a684e6/full.jpeg","excerpt":"身為超商店員，這兩天10個客人走進來有11個是要買口罩的，聽到口罩賣完的大家表情都很慌張，一直問那怎麼辦？哪邊還可以買？！，從1/28-1/30 政府每天都會釋出600萬個口罩給四大超商，每人限購三個","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"fc7574ad-e1df-43d2-bb06-8825c718c065","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-29T08:04:55.315Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-29T11:52:19.336Z","commentCount":33,"likeCount":937,"tags":[],"topics":["口罩","時事","肺炎"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":true,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"時事","forumAlias":"trending","school":"青檸香茶","department":"mizang","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":928},{"id":"011ead16-9b83-4729-9fde-c588920c6c2d","count":5},{"id":"4b018f48-e184-445f-adf1-fc8e04ba09b9","count":3},{"id":"aa0d425f-d530-4478-9a77-fe3aedc79eea","count":1}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/264cf8d5-6b8e-4013-aeb9-bf0349a684e6/full.jpeg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"dac9cab6-ab6c-447a-a497-7ba59a984c74","url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/264cf8d5-6b8e-4013-aeb9-bf0349a684e6/640.jpeg","normalizedUrl":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/264cf8d5-6b8e-4013-aeb9-bf0349a684e6/640.jpeg","thumbnail":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/264cf8d5-6b8e-4013-aeb9-bf0349a684e6/640.jpeg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":[],"createdAt":"2020-01-29T11:52:19.336Z","